Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:07.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.83,0:00:10.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這個是…
