Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:33.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他什麼襲擊尾崎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:37.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
